# Signifier (Klim Type Foundry, licensed) — must NEVER be committed to this
# PUBLIC, Apache-2.0 repo. Klim Web Font Licence §3d forbids direct download /
# third-party access to the font files; a clone-able public repo violates that,
# and committing would also imply an Apache licence the fonts don't have.
#
# The deployed site serves them from /fonts/; they're provisioned at BUILD time
# from a private source (see README). Keep local copies for dev — without them
# the landing falls back to the Georgia serif stack, which is fine for dev/OSS.
*.woff2
